Muslim disciples like this and we have

00:11:57.304 --> 00:12:07.986
many Sikh disciples, we have Parsis also
but everybody resists that. The whole society

00:12:07.986 --> 00:12:16.685
goes against that - it's true. But readily the
way Sanatan dharam has accepted Sahaja yoga,

00:12:16.685 --> 00:12:27.315
is very remarkable and that is how we are
going to penetrate into North India through

00:12:27.315 --> 00:12:33.715
Sanatan Dharam - there is no way out. Because
those who are intellectuals, don't believe in

00:12:33.715 --> 00:12:35.881
any dharam - Sanatan or Asanatan.

00:12:39.171 --> 00:12:45.081
Even the Arya Samajis won't accept Me
at all because they don't believe in deities.

00:12:52.341 --> 00:12:58.411
The openness of the Sanatan Dharam
proves that it is an Eternal religion.

00:13:01.005 --> 00:13:07.475
Because in this country thousands of
years back, many rishis and munis

00:13:08.096 --> 00:13:13.296
went into meditation to find out the
Eternal Truths of religion.

00:13:13.406 --> 00:13:21.566
It has no organization as such, and
whatever they propounded, was accepted.

00:13:24.696 --> 00:13:34.276
Afterwards, so many things went wrong.
Brahminism came into power, it corrupted

00:13:34.658 --> 00:13:45.008
practices but still, I must say, the principle
of Sanatan Dharam, could not be disturbed.

00:13:47.065 --> 00:13:53.135
You can see the result of that in this temple
and in many places where I go, is the

00:13:53.135 --> 00:14:03.712
Sanatan Dharam people who understand the
Truth. Sanatan Dharam is based on the principle

00:14:03.712 --> 00:14:13.599
of Shakti, in the Power of the Mother Goddess.
Even in Veda She is described as the

00:14:13.599 --> 00:14:22.569
Primordial Mother and She is called as
'Ee'. But the people who wanted to have an

00:14:22.569 --> 00:14:29.803
intellectual basis for that, like Arya 
Samajist, avoided all that; They didn't

00:14:29.803 --> 00:14:36.398
want to talk about it. They took that part of
Vedas, which did not deal with any deities.

00:14:39.201 --> 00:14:45.111
Now in Sahaja yoga, I've proved beyond doubt,
that we have these Deities within ourselves.

00:14:47.344 --> 00:14:53.194
Even the people, who are following Sanatan
Dharam, have to revitalize themselves

00:14:53.194 --> 00:15:01.611
and go deep into it and to find out what are
significances of all the living deities that we

00:15:01.611 --> 00:15:10.077
call of from the Mother Earth. Now, one
of the objections people have in the West,

00:15:11.310 --> 00:15:20.390
that in the Ten Commandments it is said, that 
'You should not worship any statue' - is not so.

00:15:21.402 --> 00:15:29.222
The Commandment is that, "Whatever is produced
or created by the Mother Earth or the Heavens

00:15:29.222 --> 00:15:36.560
should not be reproduced and worshiped."
What is created by Mother Earth,

00:15:37.324 --> 00:15:49.184
they don't want to find out. All the living
or we call them 'jagrut' or 'swayambhu'

00:15:49.661 --> 00:15:56.631
deities in this country, are created by
Mother Earth, so they are to be worshiped.

00:15:58.418 --> 00:16:06.038
Now this worshiping went on to such a horrible
condition, that people started producing

00:16:06.038 --> 00:16:12.014
statutes after statues, statues after statues.
For that also in Sanatan Dharma, is written

00:16:12.014 --> 00:16:16.605
"There should be a Prana Pratishtha
by a Brahmin." Clearly written.

00:16:18.198 --> 00:16:22.358
Now Prana Pratishtha by a Brahmin, it
means Brahmin who knows the Brahma -

00:16:22.403 --> 00:16:27.463
that's also clearly given. Any Dick, Tom
and Harry cannot be a Brahmin. So the

00:16:27.463 --> 00:16:32.207
Prana Pratishtha of the Deity has to be done
by a Brahmin means, he should be awakened

00:16:32.207 --> 00:16:37.027
and then it should be worshiped. But nobody
followed these rules. It went down so much

00:16:37.396 --> 00:16:42.866
that Gurunanaka had to come, Kabira had
to come and talk about the abstract God

00:16:42.866 --> 00:16:50.768
because there was no way out to cut it
short. They were great people who brought

00:16:50.768 --> 00:17:00.953
this knowledge to people but that also is
followed to such a extent that people don't

00:17:00.953 --> 00:17:07.461
want to see that the Truth lies in finding
yourself, in Atma-sakshatkar, in finding

00:17:07.461 --> 00:17:17.586
your own Spirit. So, that's how the problem
came in. He too has said that the whole universe

00:17:17.586 --> 00:17:25.611
was created by the Primordial Mother. But the
way he saw the people worshiped the deities

00:17:26.336 --> 00:17:33.456
and the way people misused it, he had to
talk of the abstract God. So that's how,

00:17:33.456 --> 00:17:39.740
we had another side of correction but
whenever you try to correct, the followers

00:17:39.740 --> 00:17:45.444
try to take it to another extreme. Like the
Sanatanies went to one extreme, these also

00:17:45.444 --> 00:17:51.254
went to another extremes but the Truth
remains the Truth. Whatever one may try to

00:17:51.254 --> 00:17:58.586
spoil it, the Truth remains the Truth. Now
Truth is to be seen, to be felt, to be

00:17:58.586 --> 00:18:03.211
experienced and to not to be believed
in your head. As I told yesterday, that

00:18:03.211 --> 00:18:10.522
mental projection cannot give you the Truth.
Supposing, you hear about Me, I'm such and such

00:18:10.522 --> 00:18:18.310
and you haven't seen Me, then what's the
use? You have to know Me personally,

00:18:19.509 --> 00:18:26.759
you have to meet Me, then only you will know
the Truth. And this is one of the reasons

00:18:26.759 --> 00:18:32.427
people can say that they did not believe
in any Gods or Goddesses and now that there are

00:18:32.427 --> 00:18:38.000
many who do not believe in any religion
whatsoever that they say there is no religion.

00:18:40.762 --> 00:18:49.902
Sahaja yoga today, is going to integrate
all of them and is going to show how

00:18:49.992 --> 00:19:00.502
all these great people, even Gurunanaka, Kabira,
Buddha, Mahavira, Rama, Krishna, Christ,

00:19:00.771 --> 00:19:08.561
Mohammad - all these people are part and
parcel of one tree and how we are fighting

00:19:08.561 --> 00:19:16.746
for nothing at all. It can be shown, it can
be proved - the condition of Sahaja yoga is,

00:19:16.746 --> 00:19:27.416
that whatever we say, has to be proved. So
this is how today, on your behalf, of the

00:19:27.416 --> 00:19:37.796
Western Sahaja yogis, specially, I thank
the organizers of this temple for showing

00:19:38.318 --> 00:19:50.208
such sense of understanding and such
great appreciation of the Truth.

