00:21:16.648 --> 00:21:24.478
[HINDI - You know that Indra had also to be
given Self realization - that's why immemorial]

00:21:24.609 --> 00:21:33.559
[HINDI - While doing all these things, in the
sixth century, when the greatest propagator]

00:21:33.559 --> 00:21:39.479
[HINDI - of Hindu religion, Adi Shankaracharya
came in this world, then he openly started talking]

00:21:39.479 --> 00:21:42.310
[HINDI - about all these things. Otherwise
we had one Bhakti marg(Devotional way)]

00:21:42.310 --> 00:21:46.607
[HINDI - and the other was the path of Vedas
by which Gayatri mantra etc were done]

00:21:48.321 --> 00:21:52.771
[HINDI - Whenever people used to be so
engrossed in Devotion that they became useless]

00:21:52.771 --> 00:21:56.094
[HINDI - then such people used to come
to pull them out of it who said,]

00:21:56.094 --> 00:22:02.328
[HINDI - "Give up devotion and take your
attention to the formless(abstract),"]

00:22:02.328 --> 00:22:06.452
[HINDI - because they were drifting so
much towards the form(idol) and when they]

00:22:06.452 --> 00:22:09.041
[HINDI - drifted too much towards the
formless, people came to to say,]

00:22:09.041 --> 00:22:12.180
[HINDI - "The Formless is not at all
helpful, we should take to the Form."]

00:22:12.209 --> 00:22:17.059
[HINDI - But the people moved like
a pendulum from here to there]

00:22:18.032 --> 00:22:25.692
[HINDI - And thus by all this the human being
understood that in this there is devotion]

00:22:25.692 --> 00:22:32.106
[HINDI - as well as abstract form
- it is Onkar as well as Krishna.

00:22:34.337 --> 00:22:37.627
[HINDI - Nothing can be gained
without this.]

00:22:40.793 --> 00:22:46.163
[HINDI - In Sahaja yoga you get the
sight(darshan) of both. You can see/view]

00:22:46.163 --> 00:22:53.170
[HINDI - the Brahma as well as all these
Gods. The Power of Brahma is the]

00:22:53.306 --> 00:23:00.906
[HINDI - Power of love of God Almighty which
moves all around us and all the living work of]

00:23:00.906 --> 00:23:07.157
[HINDI - the world, for example turning a flower
to a fruit etc, all the living work is done by it]

00:23:07.157 --> 00:23:13.384
[HINDI - It also works in us, which we call
Para Sympathetic Nervous system, in which]

00:23:13.384 --> 00:23:23.290
[HINDI - it moves and works. This is the
power of Brahma and to know this power,]

00:23:23.290 --> 00:23:31.096
[HINDI - the mechanism God has made within us,
the arrangement He has made, is very unique]

00:23:32.967 --> 00:23:45.017
[HINDI - And in order to create this
machinery, in our evolution]

00:23:45.990 --> 00:23:54.340
[HINDI - He has placed various
Gods inside our body only.]

00:23:56.283 --> 00:23:59.383
[HINDI - (ASIDE) Just remove these children
from here. They're making too much noise]

00:23:59.383 --> 00:24:07.565
[HINDI - Different Gods have been placed.
First of all He made Shri Ganesha]

00:24:09.611 --> 00:24:16.781
[HINDI - Shri Ganesha is purity. The
whole world He filled with Purity.]

00:24:16.781 --> 00:24:21.702
[HINDI - In the formless if we say, He
filled with Purity and when we talk]

00:24:21.702 --> 00:24:26.311
[HINDI - of the form, He made Shri Ganesha
- It's one and the same thing.]

00:24:27.339 --> 00:24:36.089
[HINDI - Just like you see over here, it's
burning but it has wick also as well as the light]

00:24:38.948 --> 00:24:45.268
[HINDI - In the same way, the first thing
created was Shri Ganesha, whose light]

00:24:45.268 --> 00:24:49.403
[HINDI - or radiance spreads all around,
which is the Power of God]

00:24:51.449 --> 00:24:55.489
[HINDI - Now if anyone catches hold of only
Ganeshji, that is also wrong and if anyone]

00:24:55.489 --> 00:25:00.431
[HINDI - catches hold of only the light,
is also wrong because as I told you before]

00:25:00.983 --> 00:25:08.203
[HINDI - that first He talked of the variety
of flowers and there is honey in the flowers]

00:25:08.794 --> 00:25:13.174
[HINDI - then people got stuck to the flowers
that, "Seek the flowers, seek the flowers,"]

00:25:13.174 --> 00:25:17.335
[HINDI - just started chanting, means just saying
verbally, means shabd-jalam(web of words)]

00:25:18.819 --> 00:25:25.599
[HINDI - Just started talking, then they
said, "See, the people just looking for flowers]

00:25:25.599 --> 00:25:30.461
[HINDI - have gone crazy" - worshiping the
flowers and running after them - and are]

00:25:30.461 --> 00:25:34.662
[HINDI - not talking about honey at all. Then
they said, "Okay, now let's start talking about the honey."]

00:25:34.662 --> 00:25:39.875
[HINDI - All those who have been great, only for
our benevolence took us out from one to the other]

00:25:39.875 --> 00:25:44.624
[HINDI - then again from the second to the first,
so that somehow we could become sensible]

00:25:44.624 --> 00:25:50.960
[HINDI - Sometimes talk about the formless 'Alakh
Niranjan' - a-la-kh - that which cannot been seen]

00:25:52.239 --> 00:25:57.969
[HINDI - That they started talking but that
also remained just a talk. Even if we talk]

00:25:57.969 --> 00:26:05.130
[HINDI - about the honey or madhu but how
do we find the honey? Then what should happen?]

00:26:05.130 --> 00:26:14.634
[HINDI - You should be like a bee able to suck
the honey. You yourself will have to change]

00:26:15.498 --> 00:26:22.068
[HINDI - You should have your Self-realization,
this is said in all the religions]

00:26:23.370 --> 00:26:29.500
[HINDI - because by inter-changing, it strikes
the mind of a person that if this was wrong]

00:26:29.500 --> 00:26:35.360
[HINDI - we should take to the other
thing. But all have said one thing]

